Big Mood Detector
Copyright 2024 Big Mood Detector Contributors

This product includes software developed by the Big Mood Detector Contributors.

This software incorporates work from the following research projects:

1. Seoul National University Hospital Study
   - "Accurately predicting mood episodes in mood disorder patients using wearable sleep and circadian rhythm features"
   - Published in npj Digital Medicine, 2024
   - Model weights used under research license with required citation

2. Dartmouth College PAT (Pretrained Actigraphy Transformer)
   - "AI Foundation Models for Wearable Movement Data in Mental Health Research"
   - Published 2024
   - Model weights used under research license with required citation

